vote.title: Authorize (1) a two-year interlocal Agreement with Dallas College in the amount of $1,000,000.00 for reimbursement to the City for Dallas Fire Rescue Department instructional services for the period December 10, 2025 through December 9, 2027; (2) the receipt and deposit of funds in an amount not to exceed $1,000,000.00 in the DCCCD El Centro Fund; and (3) an increase in appropriations in an amount not to exceed $1,000,000.00 in the DCCCD El Centro Fund - Financing: General Fund $240,000.00 (subject to annual appropriations); Revenue: DCCCD El Centro Fund $1,000,000.00
